<chapter id="foundation_logging_resource">
	<title>Resources</title>
	<para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					Download
				</para>
				<para>
					Download hsqldb.zip containing test DB and anyframe.example.logging.zip file containing example code
						in the following and extract those files.
						And execute start.cmd (or start.sh) file under hsqldb folder
						and start the test DB.					
					<itemizedlist>
						<listitem>
							<para>Maven-based execution</para>
							<para>
								After moving to extracted folder in the command window,
								execute command named 'mvn compile exec:java -Dexec.mainClass=...'
								and check the execution result.
								Refer to JavaDoc of Main class in each Eclipse project.							
							</para>
						</listitem>
						<listitem>
							<para>Eclipse-based execution</para>
							<para>
										After importing extracted project on Eclipse,
									select Main.java under anyframe/example/logging in src/main/java,
									and click mouth right button and click on Run As > Java Application on the context menu. Check the execution result.							
							</para>
						</listitem>									
					</itemizedlist>
				</para>
